data.description: Property is located on a large corner lot w/wrap around driveway & RV parking. The established landscaping provides a variety of vegetation & fruit trees. The backyard is fully fenced with a gazebo, deck & covered patio setting. The home comes with SS appliances & W&D. The outbuilding/shop needs a little repair but is not valued in price. This home & property has been well maintained & is in need of a fantastic owner who will give it the attention it deserves. Seller is willing to help buyer buy down rate.
